  33,33,Vi sald down your hejm do ne mingle popol excessively vi uz do en old tag ignorance! Vi observ Kontakt Prayers (Salat) don obligatory charity (Zakat) obe DI His messenger! DI wishes remove all unholiness EL VI O VI viv SANKT Shrine purify VI completely
