  33,35,submitting hom submitting women kred hom kred women obedient hom obedient women truthful hom truthful women steadfast hom steadfast women reverent hom reverent women charitable hom charitable women fast hom fast women cxast hom cxast women hom commemorate DI frequently commemorating women DI prepar them forgiveness great recompense
